WEBVTT

00:00.180 --> 00:02.940
I think we will lose this battle,
and a great many men will die.

00:04.945 --> 00:08.264
My God, Bolkonsky, what a shambles!

00:09.679 --> 00:11.295
How do you really feel about Sonya?

00:11.296 --> 00:13.303
I do love her, Tasha.

00:14.515 --> 00:17.104
I haven't been a very
affectionate husband...

00:17.105 --> 00:19.034
but it's no use saying that now.

00:21.269 --> 00:22.066
Here he is!

00:23.037 --> 00:25.904
Your wife is even more beautiful
than I remember, Bezukhov.

00:25.905 --> 00:28.824
To the health of beautiful women, Petrushka

00:28.825 --> 00:30.104
and their lovers.

00:30.105 --> 00:32.025
I challenge you!

